headline: Labcorp Expands Oncology Portfolio to Improve Patient Care and Advance Cancer Research
summary: Labcorp (NYSE: LH), a global leader of innovative and comprehensive laboratory services, announced today the expansion of its precision oncology portfolio. The additions include new test offerings for solid tumor and hematologic malignancies and enhanced biopharma solutions designed to accelerate clinical trials and companion diagnostic development.
